   Moreover, this file is also used for generating javadoc output:

     include "html_common.outlang"

     doctemplate
     " * <!-- Generated by Source-highlight -->
      * <pre><tt>
     "
     " * </tt></pre>
     "
     end

     nodoctemplate
     " * <!-- Generated by Source-highlight -->
      * <pre><tt>
     "
     " * </tt></pre>
